422
00:23:39.761 --> 00:23:41.181
I brought him home once.'

423
00:23:42.023 --> 00:23:43.969
Hey. no problem.
You just say when and we'll go.

424
00:23:47.961 --> 00:23:48.612
When.

425
00:23:49.845 --> 00:23:51.733
So you have dinner
