442
00:24:32.253 --> 00:24:34.018
You know. 'Would you like a souvenir?'

443
00:24:34.156 --> 00:24:36.541
That's how I pay the bills.
but in real life. I'm a photographer.

444
00:24:36.602 --> 00:24:38.228
I'm doing this book about the desert.

445
00:24:38.585 --> 00:24:41.700
I have five brothers.
The oldest one is Antonio.

446
00:24:41.927 --> 00:24:43.873
then Carlos. Juan.

447
00:24:44.159 --> 00:24:45.492
Miguel.

448
00:24:45.619 --> 00:24:47.586
