-Mama!
-Mi hija!

513
00:28:25.254 --> 00:28:26.895
My beautiful baby.

514
00:28:29.326 --> 00:28:30.320
Who is this?

515
00:28:30.694 --> 00:28:31.378
Um...

516
00:28:31.785 --> 00:28:34.151
Mama. Papa. this is Alex...

517
00:28:34.806 --> 00:28:35.732
Whitman.

518
00:28:35.793 --> 00:28:38.767
Mr. Fuentes. Mrs. Fuentes.
it's a pleasure to finally meet you.

519
00:28:38.828 --> 00:28:40.766
