weeks ago to build that ramp.

1353
01:12:39.236 --> 01:12:41.141
I'm afraid I'm gonna
have to shut you down.

1354
01:12:41.570 --> 01:12:43.876
Whoa. whoa. whoa. Would you excuse us...

1355
01:12:44.397 --> 01:12:45.103
