let's forget about this and go to lunch.

1363
01:13:15.109 --> 01:13:16.338
What happened?

1364
01:13:17.444 --> 01:13:18.849
Jimmy. get over here!

1365
01:13:18.910 --> 01:13:20.208
We could take my car.

1366
01:13:21.731 --> 01:13:22.744
It was a sign.

1367
01:13:23.243 --> 01:13:24.420
Of course. it was.

1368
01:13:24.600 --> 01:13:27.478
God was telling him to quit that
job and stay here with you.

1369
01:13:27.539 --> 01:13:31.202
No. Mama. It was a real sign
with neon and all that stuff.

1370
01:13:31.512 --> 01:13:32.353
Oh.

1371
01:13:32.925 --> 01:13:34.628
Then it was a miracle nobody got hurt.

1372
