It's just that the baby's due in October.

1392
01:14:34.980 --> 01:14:36.963
-And I promised...
-Is there a problem?

1393
01:14:39.619 --> 01:14:40.353
No.

1394
01:14:40.906 --> 01:14:41.767
There's no problem.

1395
01:14:55.008 --> 01:14:59.571
Alex. look what Petra and Antonio got us.
Isn't it cute?

1396
01:15:07.287 --> 01:15:09.920
We have clubs in New York.
We have clubs in Dallas.

1397
01:15:09.988 --> 01:15:12.225
We have clubs in Hawaii.
We have clubs everywhere.

1398
01:15:13.412 --> 01:15:16.062
So. with your help and with
your help and with your help.

1399
01:15:16.122 --> 01:15:20.154
I think this can be the most
successful club we've ever had. so...

1400
